extendedInfo.description: Bonus Content from the May, 2012 issue of In Tune Monthly, The Young Musician's Textbook (www.intunemonthly.com). In this app, In Tune features Lady Antebellum, their discography, and recent awards. This app also takes a close look at some of today's more unusual instruments including the harp guitar, glass harmonica and more. An In Tune Special Daily Music News feed and subscription offer is also included. In Tune Monthly, the Young Musician's Textbook, is the only magazine used as a textbook in nearly every middle and high school in the US. It's published monthly 8x/year October - May to coincide with the school year. To subscribe or learn more visit www.intunemonthly.com.
